edu.dynamic.dynamiz.parser

Enum OptionType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<OptionType>
      • edu.dynamic.dynamiz.parser.OptionType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<OptionType>

    public enum OptionType
extends java.lang.Enum<OptionType>
    OptionType enum class is a class to hold the various options applicable to many commands. Using OptionType allows the users to specify the PRIORITY, START_TIME, END_TIME, or ORDER_BY options for each items. This enum class mainly facilitates the functionalities of Command classes as well as help in Parsing of the command.
